Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.00,0:00:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's get to today's first request.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.06,0:00:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, our first request comes from the 44 y/o Shintani Kazutaka, a manager of a sports shop, who lives in Osaka.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.60,0:00:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,"Good evening, Detectives."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"For 10 years, there's been an old man that's constantly on my mind."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.40,0:00:25.26,Default,,0,0,0,,"From my eldest son to my youngest child, it's the old man that has kept passing me by every morning as I drop my child off at the nursery."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.46,0:00:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,"He sprints down the street every morning, wearing a suit & leather shoes, and carrying a bag."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.74,0:00:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,"I've never seen him stop or walk at a normal pace."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.02,0:00:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,"If it only happened once in a while, one might think 'Perhaps he's running because he's late?', but every morning for the past 10 years, he's been running fast enough to gasp for air!"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.36,0:00:46.88,Default,,0,0,0,,"Why does he run at full speed every morning?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.88,0:00:53.34,Default,,0,0,0,,"I've meant to ask him before, but he's running so frantically, I can't bring myself to stop him."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.48,0:00:57.16,Default,,0,0,0,,"Now my child will finish kindergarten soon, so I have little time left where I get to see him."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.16,0:01:02.12,Default,,0,0,0,,"Could you please resolve this mystery I've been carrying for 10 years?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.30,0:01:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,This request has really got me excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.54,0:01:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It's been happening every morning ... for 10 years!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.00,0:01:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's a situation where he can't just approach him.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.98,0:01:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,He doesn't know how it would turn out if he did.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.62,0:01:22.84,Default,,0,0,0,,So what is this old man's goal, running continuously for 10 years?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.84,0:01:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, we had a chat with him, take a look!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.48,0:01:36.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning! - Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.96,0:01:40.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm with Tantei Knight Scoop ...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.78,0:01:43.40,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. - Good morning, it's so early!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.40,0:01:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Ishida. - Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.48,0:01:49.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everyone up already? - The children are still sleeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.46,0:01:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning! Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.24,0:01:55.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning. - Have you been up all night?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.76,0:01:58.40,Default,,0,0,0,,It's always this early, honestly. - No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.64,0:02:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Preparing bento! - Ah, please, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.84,0:02:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,And what's over here, apples, ah! You're preparing fruits.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.78,0:02:10.26,Default,,0,0,0,,How old do you think he is? - Somewhere ... in his late 50s?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.26,0:02:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,And he gets there at 8 ... - Yes, around 8:22.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.00,0:02:18.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyday? - Yes, everyday.\NSeriously? - Yes, I'm serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.84,0:02:21.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I recorded him. Should we take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.06,0:02:23.18,Default,,0,0,0,,From inside your car? - Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.28,0:02:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, on such a clear and straight street?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you'd easily spot someone running towards you.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.92,0:02:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,He will appear ... is that him? - In just a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.60,0:02:45.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, it's really him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.78,0:03:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You just recorded him once? - No, well ... day after day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.44,0:03:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,328)}2nd day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.28,0:03:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is! So full of spirit!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.58,0:03:21.12,Default,,0,0,0,,It's really true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.32,0:03:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He seems a little tired today.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.00,0:03:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.42,0:03:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a different angle, but the same guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.96,0:03:31.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1133,610)}3rd day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.50,0:03:35.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(992,606)}It was a bit rainy on the 4th day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:40.70,Default,,0,0,0,,There he is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.52,0:03:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(1137,616)}5th day
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.54,0:03:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't he like a police detective?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is like "Bark at the Sun*"!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(653,35)}[*Detective drama running during the 70s and 80s]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(635,272)}Tried to combine it with "Bark at the Sun!"
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.16,0:03:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(661,37)}[Theme song of "Bark at the Sun!"]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.98,0:04:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Your wife should also see this, this is really good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.90,0:04:28.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I see him, too. And our daughter also saw him when she was running late.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.02,0:04:34.56,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why in this family ... he often gets brought up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.56,0:04:36.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That's amazing! - It's a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.40,0:04:40.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(647,368)}Everyone in this family has noticed him
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.78,0:04:40.60,Default,,0,0,0,,So at the dinner table, everyone talks about him? - That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.94,0:04:44.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, the kids. Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.40,0:04:52.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You've still got such a sleepy face!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.44,0:04:58.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You also saw the running old man, what did you think of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.30,0:05:01.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I was also running late, so it's like we were colleagues.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.40,0:05:06.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, were you running side-by-side? - No, we passed each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:09.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I see! Do you know why he's running?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.38,0:05:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I dunno ... - You dunno?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.38,0:05:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,You're still gradually waking up?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Usually, we'd just go there, stop him and go "Excuse me, this is Tantei Knight Scoop ..." ...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.98,0:05:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you reckon we can stop him? - I think if you do that, he'll be late to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.40,0:05:30.92,Default,,0,0,0,,100%. - Then that's off the table.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.66,0:05:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(640,538.572)}It might upset him if we just started recording him, so we're going to tail him first and figure out the best timing
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.04,0:05:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,So we'll only interview the running man ... once he's calmed down .
