Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.36,0:05:45.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Have a nice day! - We're going, see you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.52,0:05:50.94,Default,,0,0,0,,On this street? - That's right. - He'll come this way.
