Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.46,0:05:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,And in the direction he's running in ... - There's the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.48,0:06:03.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah and over here we saw him in the video.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.72,0:06:10.86,Default,,0,0,0,,So over here, we'll make it look like I was interviewing you ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.32,0:06:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how we'll do it, as we wait for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.92,0:06:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(507.429,537.429)}First act like they're doing a street interview, then start tailing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.14,0:06:22.94,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you think? Will we get him on tape?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.94,0:06:26.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Uwaaah... - He'll get here any moment now.
