Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,He's there! He's there! There he's running! He's made his appearance!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.52,0:06:43.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting nervous ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.16,0:06:44.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Please come this way ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.86,0:06:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,"Ah, so that's how it is!" - "Yes."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.98,0:06:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,"So, you really like Knight Scoop, then?"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.54,0:06:53.68,Default,,0,0,0,,"That's right." - "Thank you very much, that makes us very happy."
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.68,0:06:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,"Do you live in this area?" - "Yes." - "Ah, they have nice houses around here."
