Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.38,0:09:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the running person for you
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.60,0:09:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Detective Ishida speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.32,0:10:02.16,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll meet up?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.82,0:10:06.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.78,0:10:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(634.286,322.571)}Interview arranged
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.06,0:10:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,So, we've gathered everyone from the Shintani family.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.22,0:10:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,So in a few moments, he'll be coming this way. - I really want to meet him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.94,0:10:19.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanna see him! - I'm looking forward to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.66,0:10:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm looking forward to it. - I'm looking forward to resolve this.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.86,0:10:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,How can he run everyday? - Ah, he's coming this way, running!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.46,0:10:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,He's running!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.84,0:10:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop, stop, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.78,0:10:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your hard work! - Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.86,0:10:54.68,Default,,0,0,0,,These are my clients, the Shintani family. - We see you all the time!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:11:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,We noticed you because you always put so much effort into your running.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.62,0:11:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,How old are you now? - 57. - Ah, I'm glad to hear that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.56,0:11:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean? - It's just you don't see it very often close to retirement.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.58,0:11:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,So why do you run every morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.42,0:11:18.42,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry to say this, but it's because I'm running late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.92,0:11:24.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though we were deeply impressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.16,0:11:26.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you serious? - Absolutely.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.26,0:11:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Couldn't you get up 15min earlier? - Ah, I do get up early.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.82,0:11:35.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I just hate wasting time traveling.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.30,0:11:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,At Okamachi, you got off, moved to the front, and got on the train again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.60,0:11:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Every morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.04,0:11:47.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's because I'm running late.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.12,0:11:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\pos(638.857,372.857)}Showing him what his running looks like
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.88,0:11:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,You can spot yourself already
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.34,0:11:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you coming in sight? - There I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.12,0:12:01.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, there you are! You're panting.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.48,0:12:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh man ...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.94,0:12:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,You've been running constantly for 10 years.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.98,0:12:12.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you keep this up?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.22,0:12:17.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's just because I'm running late.

